	'setting_memory_tips' => '<li>Enable memory optimization function will greatly improve program performance and server load capacity. Memory optimization function requires server system and PHP extension module support</li><li>Currently supported memory optimization interfaces include Memcache, eAccelerator, Alternative PHP Cache (APC), Xcache, Redis, YAC, APCu, the optimization system will select the interface in turn according to the current server environment</li><li>The main settings of the memory interface are located in config_global.php, you can edit config_global.php by editing Make advanced settings</li>', //<li>啟用內存優化功能將會大幅度提升程序性能和服務器的負載能力，內存優化功能需要服務器系統以及PHP擴展模塊支持</li><li>目前支持的內存優化接口有 Memcache、eAccelerator、Alternative PHP Cache(APC)、Xcache、Redis、YAC、APCu，優化系統將會依據當前服務器環境依次選用接口</li><li>內存接口的主要設置位於 config_global.php 當中，您可以通過編輯 config_global.php 進行高級設置</li>
