	'setting_serveropti_jspath' => 'JS file URL', //JS 文件 URL
	'setting_serveropti_jspath_comment' => 'Sets the URL of the site\'s JS files. When set as the cache directory, the system will compress the *.js files in the default directory and save them to the cache directory to improve the reading speed', //設置站點 JS 文件的 URL。當設置為緩存目錄時，系統會將默認目錄中的 *.js 文件進行壓縮然後保存到緩存目錄以提高讀取速度
