	'setting_serveropti_delayviewcount_thread_attach' => 'Topic views and attachment downloads', //主題瀏覽量和附件下載量
	'setting_serveropti_delayviewcount_comment' => 'Delaying the update of the pageviews of attachments can significantly reduce the server load of heavily visited sites. It is recommended to enable this feature', //延遲更新附件的瀏覽量，可明顯降低訪問量很大的站點的服務器負擔，建議開啟本功能
	'setting_serveropti_nocacheheaders' => '<span class="spectitle">Disable browser buffering</span>', //<span class="spectitle">禁止瀏覽器緩衝</span>
	'setting_serveropti_nocacheheaders_comment' => 'Forbid the browser to buffer the site page, which can be used to solve the problem that the content of the browser is not refreshed normally. Note: This function will increase the load on the server', //禁止瀏覽器對站點頁面進行緩衝，可用於解決極個別瀏覽器內容刷新不正常的問題。注意: 本功能會加重服務器負擔
	'setting_serveropti_lazyload' => 'Enable delayed image loading', //開啟圖片延時加載
	'setting_serveropti_lazyload_comment' => 'When enabled, the pictures in the page are reloaded in the current window of the browser, which can significantly reduce the server burden on sites with a large number of visits. It is recommended to enable this function.', //當開啟後，頁面中的圖片在瀏覽器的當前窗口時再加載，可明顯降低訪問量很大的站點的服務器負擔，建議開啟本功能
	'setting_serveropti_blockmaxaggregationitem' => '<span class="spectitle">Participate in module aggregation data number</span>', //<span class="spectitle">參與模塊聚合數據條數</span>
	'setting_serveropti_blockmaxaggregationitem_comment' => 'This value affects the number of pieces of data retrieved by MYSQL during module aggregation. If it is set too large, it will seriously affect the performance of MYSQL. If it is set too small, it will affect the ideal level of data in the aggregation result of the module. 0 is to disable this function', //此值影響模塊聚合時MYSQL檢索數據的條數，設置太大將嚴重影響MYSQL的性能，設置太小將會影響模塊聚合結果數據的理想程度。0為關閉此功能
	'setting_serveropti_blockcachetimerange' => 'Module update time interval', //模塊更新時間區間
	'setting_serveropti_blockcachetimerange_comment' => 'Set all modules to update within the specified time interval. You can avoid peak hours of access based on website access. For example: 3:00-7:00', //設置全部模塊在指定的時間區間內更新。可以根據網站的訪問情況，避開訪問高峰時間段。如：3點-7點
	'setting_serveropti_blockcachetimerangepoint' => 'Point', //點
	'setting_serveropti_sessionclose' => 'Whether to close the session mechanism', //是否關閉session機制
	'setting_serveropti_sessionclose_comment' => 'After closing the session mechanism, the server load of the site can be significantly reduced. It is recommended to enable this function when the number of online users exceeds 20,000 (Note: the number of visitors and the online time of users will no longer be counted, and the online forum homepage and section list page will not be counted. User list feature will not be available)', //關閉session機制以後，可明顯降低站點的服務器負擔，建議在線用戶數超過2萬時開啟本功能（注意：遊客數和用戶的在線時長將不再進行統計，論壇首頁和版塊列表頁面的在線用戶列表功能將不可用）
	'setting_serveropti_onlineguestsmultiple' => 'Measured proportion of online people', //在線人數測算比例
	'setting_serveropti_onlineguestsmultiple_comment' => 'After the session mechanism is turned off, the total number of online users (including tourists and users) ≒ actual online users * the proportion of online users, the recommended value is about 10, which can be a floating point number (note: the actual online user number cache period is 600 seconds)', //關閉session機制以後，總在線人(包括遊客和用戶) ≒ 實際在線用戶數 * 在線人數測算比例，建議值為10左右,可為浮點數（注意：實際在線用戶數緩存週期為600秒）
