	'setting_accountguard' => 'Account Bodyguard', //賬號保鏢
	'setting_sec_code_tips' => '<li>Use an image as the verification code text. The image must contain 24 characters of "2346789BCEFGHJKMPQRTVWXY", and must be a GIF transparent image, with a transparent background and a black foreground. Black is the first index color of the image. The image size is not limited, but it is recommended that the width should not be greater than 1/4 of the verification code width, and the height should not be greater than the verification code height. After the production is completed, create a new subdirectory under static/image/seccode/gif/, the directory name is arbitrary, and upload the 24 GIF pictures that have been created to the new subdirectory</li><li>Use the picture as the verification code background, upload the prepared JPG image to the static/image/seccode/background/ directory, the site will randomly use the image inside as the background of the verification code</li><li>Use TTF font as the verification code text, put The downloaded TTF English font file is uploaded to the static/image/seccode/font/en/ directory, and the site will randomly use the font file inside as the text of the verification code.</li><li>Before using the Chinese image verification code, you need to Upload the TTF Chinese font file containing complete Chinese characters to the static/image/seccode/font/ch/ directory, and the site will randomly use the font file inside as the text of the verification code</li><li>The system verification code is located in source/ In the class/seccode/ directory, the plugin verification code is located in the source/plugin/plugin directory/seccode/ directory. </li>', //<li>使用圖片作為驗證碼文字，圖片必須包含字符「2346789BCEFGHJKMPQRTVWXY」24 個字符，且必須為 GIF 透明圖片、背景透明、前景黑色，黑色為圖片的第一個索引色。圖片大小不限制，但建議寬度不大於驗證碼寬度的 1/4，高度不大於驗證碼高度。製作完畢後在 static/image/seccode/gif/ 下創建一個新的子目錄，目錄名任意，把製作完畢的 24 個 GIF 圖片上傳到新子目錄下</li><li>使用圖片作為驗證碼的背景，把製作好的 JPG 圖片上傳到 static/image/seccode/background/ 目錄下，站點將隨機使用裡面的圖片作為驗證碼的背景</li><li>使用 TTF 字體作為驗證碼文字，把下載的 TTF 英文字體文件上傳到 static/image/seccode/font/en/ 目錄下，站點將隨機使用裡面的字體文件作為驗證碼的文字</li><li>使用中文圖片驗證碼前，需要把包含完整中文漢字的 TTF 中文字體文件上傳到 static/image/seccode/font/ch/ 目錄下，站點將隨機使用裡面的字體文件作為驗證碼的文字</li><li>系統驗證碼位於 source/class/seccode/ 目錄中，插件驗證碼位於 source/plugin/插件目錄/seccode/ 目錄中。</li>
	'setting_sec_qaa_tips' => '<li>Verification questions should be concise, without ambiguity, and can be answered correctly by normal people. Please update the Verification Q&A questions and answers frequently to prevent guesswork! </li><li>The system verification question and answer is located in the source/class/secqaa/ directory, and the plugin verification question and answer is located in the source/plugin/plugin directory/secqaa/ directory. </li><li>Plugin developers must read <a href="https://open.dismall.com/?!devdoc" target="_blank">Discuz! Technical Documentation</a>". </li>', //<li>驗證問題應該言簡意賅，沒有歧義，正常人都能夠正確作答。請經常更新驗證問答的問題及答案以防止被猜測！</li><li>系統驗證問答位於 source/class/secqaa/ 目錄中，插件驗證問答位於 source/plugin/插件目錄/secqaa/ 目錄中。</li><li>插件開發人員在設計新的驗證問答腳本前請務必仔細閱讀《<a href="https://open.dismall.com/?!devdoc" target="_blank">Discuz! 技術文檔</a>》中的內容。</li>
