	'setting_datetime_postignorearea' => 'A list of regions where posting is not time-limited', //發帖不受時間限制的地區列表
	'setting_datetime_postignorearea_comment' => 'When a user is at an address in this list, there is no time period for posting. One line per region, such as "Beijing" (without quotation marks), leave blank to not set. <br />Note: If you want to correctly determine the region where your IP address is located, please download the qqwry.dat IP address database file from the Internet and upload it to the "data/ipdata/" directory and rename it as wry.dat', //當用戶處於本列表中的地址時，發帖不受時間段限制。每個地區一行，例如 "北京"(不含引號)，留空為不設置。<br />注意：如要正確無誤的判斷您 IP 地址所在的地區，請到網上下載 qqwry.dat IP 地址庫文件上傳到 "data/ipdata/" 目錄下更名為 wry.dat
	'setting_datetime_postignoreip' => 'List of IPs that post without time limit', //發帖不受時間限制的IP列表
	'setting_datetime_postignoreip_comment' => 'When a user is at an IP address in this list, there is no time period for posting. One line for each IP, you can enter either the full address or just the beginning of the IP. For example, "192.168." (without quotation marks) can match all addresses in the range of 192.168.0.0 to 192.168.255.255, leave blank to not set', //當用戶處於本列表中的 IP 地址時，發帖不受時間段限制。每個 IP 一行，既可輸入完整地址，也可只輸入 IP 開頭，例如 "192.168."(不含引號) 可匹配 192.168.0.0～192.168.255.255 範圍內的所有地址，留空為不設置
	'setting_datetime_searchbanperiods' => 'Block full text search period', //禁止全文搜索時間段
	'setting_datetime_searchbanperiods_comment' => 'Users cannot use full-text search during this time period every day, the format and usage are the same as above', //每天該時間段內用戶不能使用全文搜索，格式和用法同上
	'setting_datetime_ban_downtime' => 'Block download of attachments period', //禁止下載附件時間段
	'setting_datetime_ban_downtime_comment' => 'Users cannot download attachments during this time period every day, the format and usage are the same as above', //每天該時間段內用戶不能下載附件，格式和用法同上
	'setting_sec_accountguard_forcelogin' => 'Secure login', //安全登錄
