	'setting_sec_accountguard_loginpwcheck' => 'Weak password login detection', //弱密碼登錄檢測
	'setting_sec_accountguard_loginpwcheck_comment' => 'Actions when a user logs in with a password that does not match the "Global > Registration and Access Control > Registration > Enforce Password Complexity" setting. If forced modification is enabled, accounts with weak passwords will be temporarily frozen, and will be automatically released after successful password modification.', //當用戶登錄時使用的密碼強度不符合「全局>註冊與訪問控制>註冊>強制密碼複雜度」設置時的操作。若啟用強制修改，弱密碼賬號會被暫時凍結，修改密碼成功後自動解除
