	'setting_sec_accountguard_loginoutofdate_comment' => 'When the user has logged in more than a certain period from the last time, the account will enter the unreviewed group, and the user can unfreeze the account by verifying the email address or appealing. The users who log in with QQ are not affected by this function<a href="ADMINSCRIPT?action=moderate&operation=members" >Audit users</a>', //當用戶距離上次登錄超過一定期限時，賬號會進入未審核組，用戶可以通過驗證郵箱或者申訴解凍賬號，QQ登錄的用戶不受此功能影響 <a href="ADMINSCRIPT?action=moderate&operation=members">審核用戶</a>
