	'setting_attach_basic_swfupload_comment' => 'Bulk upload adopts Flash mechanism to upload, you can upload multiple attachments at one time, and there will be progress display when uploading', //批量上傳採用 Flash 機制上傳，可一次上傳多個附件，上傳時還會有進度顯示
