	'setting_attach_image_lib' => 'Types of image processing libraries', //圖片處理庫類型
	'setting_attach_image_lib_comment' => 'Choose Discuz! Image manipulation library for thumbnails and watermarks. GD is the most extensive processing library but uses more system resources. ImageMagick is fast and takes up less system resources, but requires the server to install the ImageMagick extension. If your server has the conditions to install this program, please go to <a href="http://www.imagemagick.org" target="_blank">http://www.imagemagick.org</a> to download', //請選擇 Discuz! 用來處理縮略圖和水印的圖像處理庫。GD 是最廣泛的處理庫但是使用的系統資源較多。ImageMagick 速度快系統資源佔用少，但需要服務器安裝 ImageMagick 擴展。如果您的服務器有條件安裝此程序，請到 <a href="http://www.imagemagick.org" target="_blank">http://www.imagemagick.org</a> 下載
