	'usergroups_edit_system_buy' => 'Toll User Group', //收費用戶組
	'usergroups_edit_system_free' => 'Free User Group', //免費用戶組
	'usergroups_edit_system_public_comment' => 'Set whether it is a public user group. Note: Before using this function, please confirm whether you really need it. Otherwise, once a user joins this group, even if this group is set as a non-public user group later, users cannot be removed from this group in batches unless the user group is deleted. The public user group cannot be associated with the management group to avoid security risks', //設置是否為公眾用戶組。注意: 使用此功能前請確定是否確實需要，否則用戶一旦自行加入本組，即便之後再設置本組為非公眾用戶組，仍然無法將用戶從該組中批量去除，除非刪除本用戶組。公眾用戶組不能關聯管理組，以免產生安全隱患
	'usergroups_edit_system_dailyprice' => 'Charged public user group daily price', //收費公眾用戶組日價格
	'usergroups_edit_system_dailyprice_comment' => 'If you need users to pay the corresponding transaction points before joining this user group, please enter the daily purchase price of this group here, and the unit is the unit used for transaction points. For example, if it is set to 2, the user needs to pay 2*30=60 transaction points to purchase the permission of this group for a period of 30 days. After the 30-day validity period, the user will be automatically withdrawn from this group. If set to 0, this group is a free public user group. Note: This function is valid only after setting the user group to the public user group and setting valid transaction points', //如果您需要用戶支付相應的交易積分後才能加入本用戶組，請在此輸入本組的日購買價格，單位為交易積分所使用的單位。例如設置為 2，則用戶購買為期 30 天的本組權限，需要支付 2*30=60 個交易積分，30 天有效期後該用戶將自動從本組中退出。如設置為 0，則本組為免費公眾用戶組。注意: 本功能需要首先設定用戶組為公眾用戶組且設置了有效的交易積分後才有效
	'usergroups_edit_system_minspan' => 'Minimum purchase time (days) for a charging public user group', //收費公眾用戶組一次最短購買時間(天)
	'usergroups_edit_system_minspan_comment' => 'Set the number of transaction points worth at least one payment when the user purchases the permissions of this group. Please set the value to a value greater than or equal to 1. For example, if the daily price is 2 and the minimum purchase time is 10, then the user needs to spend at least 2*10=20 transaction points and obtain the group permission for at least 10 days before joining this group. Note: This function needs to first set the user group as the public user group to be effective.', //設置用戶在購買本組權限時，一次支付價值至少多少日的交易積分，請設置為大於等於 1 的數值。例如日價格為 2，最短購買時間為 10，則用戶至少需要花費 2*10=20 個交易積分，獲得至少 10 天本組權限，才能加入本組。注意: 本功能需要首先設定用戶組為收費公眾用戶組才有效
	'usergroups_edit_system_guest_portal_tips' => '<li>When the guest user group is set, the publishing permission related to the portal is invalid for this user group</li>', //<li>遊客用戶組設置時，門戶相關的發表權限對此用戶組無效</li>
	'usergroups_edit_system_guest_home_tips' => '<li>When the guest user group is set, the space-related publishing and commenting permissions are invalid for this user group</li>', //<li>遊客用戶組設置時，空間相關的發表、評論權限對此用戶組無效</li>
