	'usergroups_edit_special_trade_fee_comment' => 'When the transaction fee calculation method is set to a fixed value, the fee will be charged according to a fixed amount (unit: RMB). When set as a percentage, the fee will be charged as a percentage of the amount of each transaction. This function needs to set "Allow to initiate transactions", and it is valid only after setting "<a href="ADMINSCRIPT?action=ecommerce&operation=alipay">enable transaction fee</a>" in Alipay management', //交易手續費計算方式設置為固定值時，手續費將按照固定的金額(單位：人民幣 元)收取。設置為百分比時，手續費將按照每筆交易金額的百分比收取。本功能需要設置「允許發起交易」，在支付寶管理中設置「<a href="ADMINSCRIPT?action=ecommerce&operation=alipay">開啟交易手續費</a>」後才有效
