	'usergroups_edit_post_maxprice' => 'Theme (Accessories) Maximum Price', //主題(附件)最高售價
	'usergroups_edit_post_maxprice_comment' => 'The topic (attachment) sale enables authors to hide their published topics (attachments), and only when the viewer pays the author the corresponding transaction points can they view the topic (attachment) content. The maximum price allowed when users sell themes (attachments) is set here, and 0 means that users are not allowed to sell. Note: This feature can only be used after enabling Trading Points in Global Settings. If the moderator and administrator\'s selling theme (attachment) function is enabled, please set the maximum price to be higher than the maximum price allowed by ordinary user groups, so that when the post is edited, the selling price of the theme (attachment) will not be lowered rigidly.', //主題(附件)出售使得作者可以將自己發表的主題(附件)隱藏起來，只有當瀏覽者向作者支付相應的交易積分後才能查看主題(附件)內容。此處設置用戶出售主題(附件)時允許設置的最高價格，0 為不允許用戶出售。注意: 本功能需在 全局設置中啟用交易積分後才可使用。如開啟版主及管理員的出售主題(附件)功能，請將其最高價格設置為高於普通用戶組允許的最高價格，這樣在帖子被編輯時不至於導致主題(附件)售價的硬性下調
