	'misc_stamp_listtips' => '<li>The authentication stamp is displayed on the post content page, and the authentication icon is displayed on the topic list page. </li><li>The system reserves 100 subject identification image positions, which are image IDs 0 to 99. </li><li>Do not modify the image ID arbitrarily, otherwise the stamps and icons used in the theme will be confused. </li><li>When a stamp is set with an associated operation, the stamp will be automatically added to the topic when the corresponding operation is performed; when a stamp is set with an associated icon, the icon will be automatically added to the topic list when the stamp is added. The associated action cannot be set at the same time as the associated icon. </li>', //<li>鑒定圖章顯示在帖子內容頁，鑒定圖標顯示在主題列表頁。</li><li>系統預留了 100 個主題鑒定圖片位置，分別為圖片 ID 0 至 99。</li><li>不要隨意修改圖片 ID，否則將會導致主題中已使用的圖章、圖標錯亂。</li><li>當圖章設置了關聯操作後，圖章會在執行相應操作時被自動添加到主題中；當圖章設置了關聯圖標後，圖標會在添加圖章時自動添加到主題列表中。關聯操作不可與關聯圖標同時設置。</li>
