	'db_import_tips' => '<li>This function will completely overwrite the original data while restoring the backup data. Please make sure that the site has been closed before the restoration, and the site can be reopened after the restoration is complete. </li><li><font color="blue"><b>For security reasons, we strongly recommend that you restore the database backup file after deleting the file or setting the file to be inaccessible via URL. </b></font></li><li>Before restoring data, please find the restore.php file in the utility folder of the Discuz! installation file directory, and then upload the restore.php file to the program folder data directory . <b>For the safety of your site, be sure to delete the restore.php file in time after a successful data recovery. </b></li><li>You can view the detailed information of the site\'s backup files in the data backup record, delete the expired backups, and import the required backups. </li>', //<li>本功能在恢復備份數據的同時，將全部覆蓋原有數據，請確定恢復前已將站點關閉，恢復全部完成後可以將站點重新開放。</li><li><font color="blue"><b>出於安全考慮，我們強烈建議您恢複數據庫備份文件後刪除文件或設置文件不可通過 URL 訪問。</b></font></li><li>恢複數據前請在 Discuz! 安裝文件目錄下 utility 文件夾內找到 restore.php 文件，然後將 restore.php 文件上傳到程序文件夾data目錄下。<b>為了您站點的安全，成功恢複數據後請務必及時刪除 restore.php 文件。</b></li><li>您可以在數據備份記錄處查看站點的備份文件的詳細信息，刪除過期的備份,並導入需要的備份。</li>
