	'db_runquery_tips' => '<li>You can add common SQL operations for functional expansion by modifying /source/admincp/admincp_quickquery.php. </li><li>For security reasons, Discuz! prohibits the direct execution of SQL statements by default in the background, and can only use the content of common SQL.<br />If you want to write SQL upgrade statements at will, you need to configure the config Change the $_config[admincp][runquery] setting in /config_global.php to 1. </li>', //<li>您可以通過修改 /source/admincp/admincp_quickquery.php 來添加常用 SQL 操作進行功能擴充。</li><li>出於安全考慮，Discuz! 後台默認情況下禁止 SQL 語句直接執行，只能使用常用 SQL 當中的內容，<br />如果您想自己隨意書寫 SQL 升級語句，需要將 config/config_global.php 當中的 $_config[admincp][runquery] 設置修改為 1。</li>
