	'adv_type_version' => 'Module version', //模塊版本
	'adv_type_headerbanner' => 'Header banner ads', //頁頭通欄廣告
	'adv_type_headerbanner_tips' => '<li>Display method: Header banner ads are displayed at the top right of the forum page, usually in the form of 468x60 images or Flash. When there are multiple header banner ads on the current page, the system will randomly select one of them to display. </li><li>Value Analysis: Because it can display the content of the advertisement in the most conspicuous position as soon as the page is opened, it has become one of the types of advertisements with the highest price and the most suitable for commercial promotion or brand promotion. . </li>', //<li>展現方式: 頁頭通欄廣告顯示於論壇頁面右上方，通常使用 468x60 圖片或 Flash 的形式。當前頁面有多個頁頭通欄廣告時，系統會隨機選取其中之一顯示。</li><li>價值分析: 由於能夠在頁面打開的第一時間將廣告內容展現於最醒目的位置，因此成為了網頁中價位最高、最適合進行商業宣傳或品牌推廣的廣告類型之一。</li>
	'adv_type_footerbanner' => 'Footer banner ads', //頁尾通欄廣告
	'adv_type_footerbanner_tips' => '<li>Display method: The footer banner ads are displayed in the lower part of the forum page, usually in the form of 468x60 or other size images and Flash. When there are multiple footer banner ads on the current page, the system will randomly select one of them to display. </li><li>Value analysis: Compared with the head and middle of the page, the display probability of the tail of the page is relatively low, which usually does not arouse the disgust of the visitors, and can basically cover all the audiences who are interested in the advertising content. , thus suitable for neutral and moderate promotion. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 頁尾通欄廣告顯示於論壇頁面中下方，通常使用 468x60 或其他尺寸圖片、Flash 的形式。當前頁面有多個頁尾通欄廣告時，系統會隨機選取其中之一顯示。</li><li>價值分析: 與頁面頭部和中部相比，頁面尾部的展現機率相對較低，通常不會引起訪問者的反感，同時又基本能夠覆蓋所有對廣告內容感興趣的受眾，因此適合中性而溫和的推廣。</li>
	'adv_type_text' => 'In-page text ads', //頁內文字廣告
	'adv_type_text_tips' => '<li>Display method: In-page text ads are displayed in the form of a table at the top of the three pages of the homepage, topic list and post content, usually in the form of text, but also small pictures and Flash. When there are multiple text ads on the current page, the system will display them all in the form of a table according to the set display order. At the same time, the number of columns in the table can be dynamically arranged in the range of 3 to 5, so as to automatically achieve the best advertisement arrangement effect. </li><li>Value Analysis: Since this type of advertisement is usually displayed in the form of text, but its position on the upper page makes this type of advertisement one of the must-read contents for visitors. The same page can present as many as a dozen text advertisements, which also determines that it is a popular but cost-effective promotion method, and can also be used for the forum\'s own publicity and announcements. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 頁內文字廣告以表格的形式，顯示於首頁、主題列表和帖子內容三個頁面的中上方，通常使用文字的形式，也可使用小圖片和 Flash。當前頁面有多個文字廣告時，系統會以表格的形式按照設定的顯示順序全部展現，同時能夠對表格列數在 3～5 的範圍內動態排布，以自動實現最佳的廣告排列效果。</li><li>價值分析: 由於此類廣告通常以文字形式展現，但其所在的較靠上的頁面位置，使得此類廣告成為了訪問者必讀的內容之一。同一頁面可以呈現多達十幾條文字廣告的特性，也決定了它是一種平民化但性價比較高的推廣方式，同時還可用於論壇自身的宣傳和公告之用。</li>
	'adv_type_thread' => 'In-post ads', //帖內廣告
	'adv_type_thread_tips' => '<li>Display method: In-post advertisements are displayed above, below or to the right of the post content. The above and below the post content are usually in the form of text, and the right side of the post content is usually in the form of pictures. When there are multiple in-post advertisements on the current page, the system will select items equal to the number of posts per page and display them randomly. You can modify the number of ads shown per post in other settings in Global settings. </li><li>Value analysis: Since the post is the core part of the forum, the in-post advertisement embedded in the post content can be naturally accepted when the user browses the post content. For the effective promotion of specific content, it can also be used for the promotion and announcement of the forum itself. It is recommended to set up multiple in-post ads to differentiate the ad content and attract more visitors\' attention. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 帖內廣告顯示於帖子內容的上方、下方或右方，帖子內容的上方和下方通常使用文字的形式，帖子內容右方通常使用圖片的形式。當前頁面有多個帖內廣告時，系統會從中抽取與每頁帖數相等的條目進行隨機顯示。您可以在 全局設置中的其他設置中修改每帖顯示的廣告數量。</li><li>價值分析: 由於帖子是論壇最核心的組成部分，嵌入帖子內容內部的帖內廣告，便可在用戶瀏覽帖子內容時自然的被接受，加上隨機播放的特性，適合於特定內容的有效推廣，也可用於論壇自身的宣傳和公告之用。建議設置多條帖內廣告以實現廣告內容的差異化，從而吸引更多訪問者的注意力。</li>
	'adv_type_interthread' => 'Advertisement between posts', //帖間通欄廣告
	'adv_type_interthread_tips' => '<li>Presentation: The inter-post banner is displayed between the thread post and the first reply, and can use 468x60 or other size images and Flash. When there are multiple inter-post banner ads on the current page, the system will randomly select one of them to display. </li><li>Value analysis: Because it can separate the topic from the reply post, the advertisement size is large and does not affect the content of the post, so it will not arouse the objection of post authors and visitors, and is suitable for commercial promotion or brand promotion in the post. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 帖間通欄廣告顯示於主題帖和第一個回帖之間，可使用 468x60 或其他尺寸圖片和 Flash 的形式。當前頁面有多個帖間通欄廣告時，系統會隨機選取其中之一顯示。</li><li>價值分析: 由於能夠將主題與回帖分開，廣告尺寸大而且不影響帖子內容，因此不會招致帖子作者及訪問者反感，適合在帖內進行商業宣傳或品牌推廣。</li>
	'adv_type_float' => 'Floating ad', //漂浮廣告
	'adv_type_float_tips' => '<li>Display method: The floating advertisement is displayed in the lower left corner of the page. When the page is scrolled, the advertisement will move by itself to maintain the original position, usually in the form of small pictures or Flash. When there are multiple floating ads on the current page, the system will randomly select one of them to display. </li><li>Value Analysis: Floating ads are an effective means of strong commercial promotion, and their floating nature on the page makes them easier to pay attention to than fixed pictures and texts. This obligatory attention may also lead to resentment from visitors who are not interested in the content of the ad. Please be careful not to display overly large images or Flash in the form of floating ads, so as not to affect the reading of the page. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 漂浮廣告展現於頁面左下角，當頁面滾動時廣告會自行移動以保持原來的位置，通常使用小圖片或 Flash 的形式。當前頁面有多個漂浮廣告時，系統會隨機選取其中之一顯示。</li><li>價值分析: 漂浮廣告是進行強力商業推廣的有效手段，其在頁面中的浮動性，使其與固定的圖片和文字相比，更容易被關注，正因為如此，這種強制性的關注也可能招致對此廣告內容不感興趣的訪問者的反感。請注意不要將過大的圖片或 Flash 以漂浮廣告的形式顯示，以免影響頁面閱讀。</li>
	'adv_type_couplebanner' => 'Couplet ad', //對聯廣告
	'adv_type_couplebanner_tips' => '<li>Display method: The couplet advertisement is displayed in the form of a rectangular picture on both sides of the top of the page, which looks like a couplet, usually in the form of a wide, small and tall rectangular picture or Flash. The couplet advertisement is generally only used when the width of the main table is specified by pixels. If the width of the main table is specified by a percentage of more than 90%, it may affect the normal browsing of visitors. This type of ad is automatically not displayed when the visitor\'s browser width is less than 800 pixels. When there are multiple couplet advertisements on the current page, the system will randomly select one of them to display. </li><li>Value Analysis: Since couplet ads are only displayed on both sides of the high-resolution (1024x768 or higher) screen and only occupy the blank area of the page, they will not arouse visitors\' disgust and can be well promoted content. However, due to the special requirements on the resolution and the width of the main table, the audience ratio of the ad cannot reach 100%. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 對聯廣告以長方形圖片的形式顯示於頁面頂部兩側，形似一幅對聯，通常使用寬小高大的長方形圖片或 Flash 的形式。對聯廣告一般只在使用像素約定主表格寬度的情況下使用，如使用超過 90% 以上的百分比約定主表格寬度時，可能會影響訪問者的正常瀏覽。當訪問者瀏覽器寬度小於 800 像素時，自動不顯示此類廣告。當前頁面有多個對聯廣告時，系統會隨機選取其中之一顯示。</li><li>價值分析: 對聯廣告由於只展現於高分辨率(1024x768 或更高)屏幕的兩側，只佔用頁面的空白區域，因此不會招致訪問者反感，能夠良好的突出推廣內容。但由於對分辨率和主表格寬度的特殊要求，使得廣告的受眾比例無法達到 100%。</li>
	'adv_type_intercat' => 'Inter-classified advertising', //分類間廣告
	'adv_type_intercat_tips' => '<li>Presentation method: The inter-category advertisement is displayed between two adjacent forum categories on the forum homepage, and can use 468x60 or other size images and Flash formats. When there are multiple inter-classified advertisements on the current page, the system will randomly select items equal to the number of forum classifications and display them randomly. </li><li>Value analysis: Because it appears in a more obvious position on the forum homepage, the advertisement display effect is good, but too many homepage advertisements may cause visitors to be disgusted. </li>', //<li>展現方式: 分類間廣告顯示於論壇首頁相鄰的兩個論壇分類之間，可使用 468x60 或其他尺寸圖片和 Flash 的形式。當前頁面有多個分類間廣告時，系統會從中抽取與論壇分類數相等的條目進行隨機顯示。</li><li>價值分析:由於出現在論壇首頁比較明顯的位置，廣告展示效果較好，但是過多過大的首頁廣告可能會招致訪問者反感。 </li>
